The paper deals with haptic-assisted virtual assembly and prototyping, which involves computer graphics, robotics, computer vision, multimedia, and control systems. Therefore, cs.GR (Graphics), cs.RO (Robotics), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.MM (Multimedia), and cs.SY (Systems and Control) are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories that this paper belongs to.
